DESCRIPTION:<p>We are kicking off our 2025 Year End Performance Review Cycl
 e\, and this training session will walk you through how to use the performa
 nce review tools in Rippling. We are offering two training sessions. You on
 ly need to attend one session. The meeting will be recorded and shared afte
 rward for those who are unable to attend live. </p><p>Note: Employees who j
 oined on or after October 31 are not included in this review cycle and ther
 efore are not required to attend this training session.<br></p>\n\n-::~:~::
