 ey need to calculate the Voting Index? Are we gonna track the PAC money? If
  not\, how should we get that info?<br></li><li>Do we have necessary API en
 dpoints from Polymarket &amp\; StandWithCrypto for data?<br></li><li>What d
 oes editorial &amp\; media team strategy look like for coverage? Which sect
 ions to reserve for articles/podcasts/short videos?</li></ul>\n\n-::~:~::~:
