CREATED:20251028T205439Z
DESCRIPTION:<h3 dir="ltr"><b><i>Context</i></b></h3><p dir="ltr"><i>The Blo
 ck’s website has grown and evolved over time as new products\, features\, a
 nd content types have been added. That growth has made the experience riche
 r but also more complex. Different sections have taken on different design 
 styles\, the mobile experience has fallen behind\, and it has become harder
  for users to move seamlessly between news\, research\, learn content\, and
  company data.</i></p><p dir="ltr"><i>The redesign is meant to simplify and
  strengthen the foundation of The Block. It will bring consistency\, make t
 he site faster\, improve discovery\, and help us build for the next phase o
 f growth across audience\, revenue\, and technology.</i></p><p dir="ltr"><i
 >Before making design or product decisions\, we’re starting with internal c
 onversations to understand how teams across The Block view the current site
 \, what is working well\, and where there is room to improve.</i></p><h3 di
 r="ltr"><b><i>Purpose</i></b></h3><p dir="ltr"><i>These interviews are mean
 t to collect open feedback from across the company. The goal is to learn ho
 w people experience the site in their daily work\, how they believe users e
 ngage with The Block\, and what would make the platform stronger moving for
 ward.</i></p><p dir="ltr"><i>There are no right answers. We want honest per
 spectives that can help shape priorities\, identify opportunities\, and ens
 ure the redesign reflects the needs of the full business.</i></p>\n\n-::~:~
 ::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~::
 ~:~::-\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/wdj-wmns-uxt\nOr dia
 l: (US) +1 573-568-8116 PIN: 263657246#\nMore phone numbers: https://tel.me
 et/wdj-wmns-uxt?pin=5096115447629&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https:/
 /support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720\n\nPlease do not edit this secti
 on.\n-::~:~::~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:~:
 ~:~:~:~:~::~:~::-
